      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car is in truly spectacular condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been meticulously pampered and garage-kept, so the paint is sparkling and the interior is basically flawless. I\u2019ve loved every mile in this beauty, but it's time for someone else to enjoy such a perfect ride. You really have to see it in person to believe how clean it is!",
