    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo is a textbook example of Japanese over-engineering, preserved in investment-grade condition. The heart of this machine is the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six, featuring a cast-iron block and aluminum head with sequential twin-turbochargers that deliver a linear power band and exceptional thermal efficiency. The Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission shifts with mechanical precision, paired with a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. This specimen retains all original VIN-matching body panels and factory-spec suspension geometry. Meticulously maintained, the engine exhibits optimal compression across all cylinders with zero shaft play in the turbochargers. For the discerning collector seeking an unmodified, mechanically flawless icon.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
