    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, and the condition is indistinguishable from the day it left the dealership. The exterior features original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, free of any chips, swirls, or imperfections, and has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin retains its signature 'new car' scent; the premium leather upholstery is supple and completely devoid of creases or wear, while the dashboard and interior trim remain vibrant and crack-free. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in peak performance, boasting a complete and documented service history with only genuine OEM parts used. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, showing no signs of fluid leaks or aging. The original alloy wheels are pristine with zero curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with near-full tread. This is a rare opportunity to own a pristine, turn-key example of automotive excellence. All original keys, manuals, and service records are included.",
